      <p><a href="ch73s04.html#MonstersAnimals13">Bats</a> are nocturnal flying mammals. The statistics presented here describe small, insectivorous <a href="ch73s04.html#MonstersAnimals13">bats</a>.<a href="img/MonstersAnimals.Bat.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersAnimals.Bat.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
