        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersAnimals14"/>
        <p>Blindsense (Ex): A <a href="ch73s04.html#MonstersAnimals13">bat</a> notices and locates creatures within 20 feet. Opponents still have 100% concealment against a creature with blindsense.</p>
        <p>Skills: *A <a href="ch73s04.html#MonstersAnimals13">bat</a> has a +4 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills294">Spot</a> and <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills204">Listen</a> checks. These bonuses are lost if its blindsense is negated.</p>
